290
00:31:13,600 --> 00:31:15,045
現在，看看這裡
{\fs12}Now, look here.{\r}

291
00:31:15,120 --> 00:31:18,681
你可以叫我去死，但你不能嘲笑我
{\fs12}You can tell me to go to the devil, but you can't laugh at me.{\r}

292
00:31:24,880 --> 00:31:29,807
詛咒襲擊了她，現在經由她，它將攻擊我兒子
{\fs12}The curse has struck her, and now, through her, it will strike my son.{\r}

293
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:31,041
安靜
{\fs12}Quiet.{\r}

294
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:34,930
法蘭克，你去你父親的書房好嗎？
{\fs12}Frank, will you come to your father's study?{\r}

295
00:31:35,600 --> 00:31:38,524
海倫，我會親自送你回家
{\fs12}Helen, I shall take you home presently.{\r}

296
00:31:42,360 --> 00:31:44,362
我馬上就回來
{\fs12}I'll be back in a minute.{\r}

297
00:31:55,240 --> 00:31:57,083
印和闐還活著...
{\fs12}Imhotep was alive{\r}

298
00:31:57,160 --> 00:32:00,164
當那個在博物館的木乃伊是神殿的女祭司
{\fs12}when that mummy in the museum was a vestal virgin in the temple.{\r}

299
00:32:00,240 --> 00:32:03,687
三千七百年前！現在和我們有什麼關係？
{\fs12}Thirty-seven hundred years ago! What's that got to do with us, now?{\r}

300
00:32:03,760 --> 00:32:05,922
你的助手，他瘋狂的死了...
