302
00:32:08,480 --> 00:32:11,404
做了該捲軸一部分的轉譯*
{\fs12}made a transcription of part of that scroll.{\r}

303
00:32:11,480 --> 00:32:14,370
是。仍然在我手上
{\fs12}Yes. I have it still.{\r}

304
00:32:14,440 --> 00:32:16,807
你似乎認為這東西，什麼妖魔鬼怪在裡面
{\fs12}You seem to think this thing has all the devils of Hell in it.{\r}

305
00:32:16,880 --> 00:32:19,167
為什麼不燒了它，一了百了？
{\fs12}Why not burn it and be done with it?{\r}

306
00:32:19,240 --> 00:32:21,208
一個優秀的建議
{\fs12}An excellent suggestion.{\r}

307
00:32:22,040 --> 00:32:24,566
印和闐的木乃伊後來怎樣了？
{\fs12}What became of the mummy of Imhotep?{\r}

308
00:32:25,720 --> 00:32:27,404
被人偷走了
{\fs12}Somebody stole it.{\r}

309
00:32:29,135 --> 00:32:31,535
看這裡，穆勒博士。格羅夫納小姐怎麼了？
{\fs12}Look here, Dr. Muller. What's the matter with Miss Grosvenor?{\r}

310
00:32:31,560 --> 00:32:35,042
你仍然認為木乃伊被偷了，約瑟夫爵士？
{\fs12}You still think that that mummy was stolen, Sir Joseph?{\r}

311
00:32:36,360 --> 00:32:37,646
是的，我...
{\fs12}Yes, I...{\r}

312
00:32:39,880 --> 00:32:41,041
哦，我不知道
