377
00:38:28,080 --> 00:38:29,730
甚為有趣
{\fs12}Most interesting.{\r}

378
00:38:30,400 --> 00:38:32,801
我可以看看那捲軸，約瑟夫爵士？
{\fs12}May I see that scroll, Sir Joseph?{\r}

379
00:38:33,960 --> 00:38:36,770
我們把它留在博物館了
{\fs12}We left it at the museum.{\r}

380
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:38,367
這樣啊
{\fs12}So.{\r}

381
00:38:38,920 --> 00:38:42,288
我有別樣東西躍給你看，一張照片
{\fs12}I have something else to show you. A photograph.{\r}

382
00:38:47,640 --> 00:38:49,927
為什麼要向我展示這些？
{\fs12}Why do you show all this to me?{\r}

383
00:38:51,040 --> 00:38:54,044
木乃伊不是被偷走的，你覺得這能想像嗎？
{\fs12}Do you think it conceivable that the mummy was not stolen,{\r}

