you know that you cannot harm me.{\r}

391
00:39:24,080 --> 00:39:27,801
你也知道你必須
將滾動歸還給我或死去。
{\fs12}You also know that you must
return that scroll to me or die.{\r}

392
00:39:29,080 --> 00:39:32,880
現在告訴那個弱小的傻瓜
滾動，無論在哪裡，
{\fs12}Now tell that weak fool to get
that scroll, wherever it is,{\r}

393
00:39:32,960 --> 00:39:36,009
並把它交給
他的努比亞僕人。
