394
00:39:36,960 --> 00:39:38,041
努比亞人！
{\fs12}The Nubian!{\r}

395
00:39:38,120 --> 00:39:40,088
古老的血統。
{\fs12}The ancient blood.{\r}

396
00:39:42,160 --> 00:39:44,527
所以你創造了他
你的奴隸。
{\fs12}So you have made him
your slave.{\r}

397
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:48,770
如果我可以抓住你，
{\fs12}If I could get my hands on you,{\r}

398
00:39:49,600 --> 00:39:53,002
我打破你的
肉乾成碎。
{\fs12}I'd break your
dried flesh to pieces.{\r}

399
00:39:56,200 --> 00:39:58,248
但是你的力量太強了。
{\fs12}But your power is too strong.{\r}

400
00:40:14,240 --> 00:40:17,483
這是邪惡的力量
