{\fs12}This is the evil force that
has been attacking her.{\r}

401
00:40:17,600 --> 00:40:19,841
男人，燒了捲軸。
燒掉它吧！
{\fs12}Burn the scroll, man.
Burn it!{\r}

402
00:40:20,600 --> 00:40:23,888
這是通過你
恐怖的存在。
{\fs12}It was through you this
horror came into existence.{\r}

403
00:40:23,960 --> 00:40:27,248
這是真的。
這是真的。
