事後筋疲力盡。
{\fs12}You're always so
exhausted afterwards.{\r}

550
00:58:15,840 --> 00:58:18,446
她太弱了無法移除，
除了去醫院。
{\fs12}She's too weak to be removed,
except to a hospital.{\r}

551
00:58:18,520 --> 00:58:21,490
我堅持讓她留在這裡
根據我們的直接觀察。
{\fs12}I insist on keeping her here
under our direct observation.{\r}

552
00:58:21,600 --> 00:58:23,682
但LeBarron博士，你沒有
告訴我們該為她做些什麼。
{\fs12}But Dr. LeBarron, you haven't
told us what to do for her.{\r}

553
00:58:23,760 --> 00:58:25,330
她每天都變弱了。
{\fs12}She's getting weaker every day.{\r}

554
00:58:25,400 --> 00:58:27,482
你知道那個便服
我在巴黎買？
{\fs12}You know that negligee
I bought in Paris?{\r}

555
00:58:27,560 --> 00:58:30,166
幫幫我穿上，
把我的廁所帶給我。
{\fs12}Help me to put it on,
and bring me my toilet things.{\r}

556
00:58:30,240 --> 00:58:32,527
我想要一些顏色。
我想好看。
{\fs12}I want some color.
I want to look well.{\r}

557
00:58:32,600 --> 00:58:35,600
但親愛的，你不能這樣做。他們會
從不允許它。護士會...
{\fs12}But you can't do that, my dear. They'd
never allow it. The nurse would be...{\r}

558
00:58:35,640 --> 00:58:37,927
我知道。
我們會擺脫她
{\fs12}I know.
We'll get rid of her.{\r}

559
00:58:38,000 --> 00:58:40,287
這是一個情節，
就在我們之間
{\fs12}This is a plot,
just between us.{\r}

560
00:58:40,360 --> 00:58:43,887
我想看看我做的方式。
對法蘭克來說，這真是一個驚喜
{\fs12}I want to look the way I did.
Just a surprise, for Frank.{\r}

561
00:58:43,960 --> 00:58:47,203
我希望你把他帶到我身邊。
你明白？
{\fs12}And I want you to bring him to me.
You understand?{\r}

562
00:58:47,960 --> 00:58:50,930
總之，我失敗了
做出診斷。
{\fs12}In short, I have failed
to make a diagnosis.{\r}

563
00:58:51,000 --> 00:58:54,129
醫學無助
在這種情況下。
{\fs12}Medical science is helpless
in a case like this.{\r}

564
00:58:54,600 --> 00:58:55,806
法蘭克
{\fs12}Frank.{\r}

565
00:58:57,800 --> 00:59:00,201
去找她，然後
不要生我的氣。
{\fs12}Go to her, and
don't be angry with me.{\r}

566
00:59:00,280 --> 00:59:02,169
我無法抗拒她。
{\fs12}I couldn't resist her.{\r}

567
00:59:05,880 --> 00:59:07,723
哦，但海倫，你
不應該這樣做。
{\fs12}Oh, but Helen, you
shouldn't have done this.{\r}

568
00:59:07,800 --> 00:59:09,086
他們不應該讓你。
{\fs12}They shouldn't have let you.{\r}

569
00:59:09,160 --> 00:59:12,209
就這一次。
也許是最後一次。
{\fs12}Just this once.
Perhaps the last time.{\r}

570
00:59:12,280 --> 00:59:14,123
但是你會好起來的。
{\fs12}But you're going to get well.{\r}

571
00:59:14,200 --> 00:59:16,248
然後我知道我可以
讓你愛我
{\fs12}Then I know I can
make you love me.{\r}

572
00:59:16,320 --> 00:59:18,482
我知道我可以讓你快樂。
{\fs12}I know I can make you happy.{\r}

573
00:59:22,480 --> 00:59:26,280
法蘭克，我愛你。
而我正在努力證明這一點，
{\fs12}I do love you, Frank.
And I'm trying to prove it,{\r}

574
00:59:26,360 --> 00:59:29,409
因為我寧願死
生活，失去你。
{\fs12}because I'd rather die
than live and lose you.{\r}

575
00:59:29,480 --> 00:59:33,201
但是你要活著。我們
不會相互失去。
{\fs12}But you're going to live. We're
not going to lose each other.{\r}

576
00:59:34,480 --> 00:59:36,482
所以，親愛的...
別罵我。
{\fs12}So, my dear...
Don't scold me.{\r}

577
00:59:36,560 --> 00:59:40,485
只是女人味的虛榮心。一世
我想再次看起來最好。
{\fs12}Just feminine vanity. I
wanted to look my best again.{\r}

578
00:59:40,560 --> 00:59:42,961
所以你知道的不僅僅是
我意識到你知道。
{\fs12}So you know more than
I realized you knew.{\r}

579
00:59:43,040 --> 00:59:44,041
你什麼意思？
{\fs12}What do you mean?{\r}

580
00:59:44,120 --> 00:59:47,442
這些衝動要發給他。
{\fs12}These impulses to go to him.{\r}

581
00:59:47,560 --> 00:59:50,530
拉力過大
承受和生活。
{\fs12}The pull is too strong
to withstand and live.{\r}

582
00:59:50,600 --> 00:59:52,682
我很高興你理解。
{\fs12}I'm so glad you understand.{\r}

583
00:59:54,000 --> 00:59:55,081
海倫知道。
{\fs12}Helen knows.{\r}

584
00:59:55,160 --> 00:59:57,003
她知道這一刻
她停止掙扎，
{\fs12}She knows the moment
she stops struggling,{\r}

585
00:59:57,080 --> 00:59:59,401
他會把她還給她
她有力量來找他。
{\fs12}he will give her back
her strength to come to him.{\r}

586
00:59:59,480 --> 01:00:01,608
但我不想
失去了自己的想法
{\fs12}But I don't want to
lose my own mind{\r}

587
01:00:01,680 --> 01:00:04,445
並成為別人，
我討厭的人。
{\fs12}and be someone else,
someone I hate.{\r}

588
01:00:04,520 --> 01:00:07,410
我親愛的，而你
變得越來越糟
{\fs12}My dear, while you
were growing worse,{\r}

589
01:00:07,480 --> 01:00:10,324
我們試圖找到他
並失敗了。
{\fs12}we tried to find him
and failed.{\r}

590
01:00:10,400 --> 01:00:13,370
下次打電話
來吧，去找他。
{\fs12}The next time the call
comes, go to him.{\r}

591
01:00:18,160 --> 01:00:20,766
穆勒，我們現在能做什麼？
{\fs12}Muller, what can we do now?{\r}

592
01:00:20,840 --> 01:00:24,367
我們不能再做了。
阿德斯.貝打敗了我。
{\fs12}We can do no more.
Ardeth has beaten me.{\r}

593
01:00:24,440 --> 01:00:27,284
下次他吸引她
對他來說，我們必須跟著她。
{\fs12}The next time he draws her
to him, we must follow her.{\r}

594
01:00:27,360 --> 01:00:28,691
然後？
{\fs12}And then?{\r}

595
01:00:29,120 --> 01:00:30,531
我們會毀了他。
{\fs12}We will destroy him.{\r}

596
01:00:56,200 --> 01:00:59,886
我給了她一些溴化物。她
現在睡著了。我會去睡覺
{\fs12}I've given her some bromide. She's
asleep now. I'll go to bed.{\r}

597
01:00:59,960 --> 01:01:02,042
行。我會在這裡等到博士
穆勒來了。
{\fs12}All right. I'll wait here till Dr.
Muller comes.{\r}

598
01:01:02,120 --> 01:01:04,088
晚安。
晚安。
{\fs12}Good night.
Good night.{\r}

599
01:03:03,200 --> 01:03:04,611
我們在哪？
{\fs12}Where are we?{\r}

600
01:03:05,320 --> 01:03:09,530
這是我的床，但這不是
寺廟也不是我父親的宮殿。
{\fs12}This is my bed, but this is not the
temple nor my father's palace.{\r}

601
01:03:09,600 --> 01:03:11,807
不要看，安克蘇娜姆
{\fs12}Do not look,
Anck-es-en-Amon.{\r}

602
01:03:12,360 --> 01:03:14,044
不要害怕。
{\fs12}Do not be afraid.{\r}

603
01:03:15,040 --> 01:03:16,530
我很害怕。

{\fs12}I was afraid.{\r}

604
01:03:17,760 --> 01:03:22,243
當你跪在我的床邊時，
面紗從我的眼睛里傳來。黑暗
{\fs12}When you were kneeling beside my bed,
a veil came over my eyes. Darkness.{\r}

605
01:03:22,360 --> 01:03:25,648
你最後的記憶是我的
在你死亡的那一刻
{\fs12}Your last memory is of me
in the hour of your death{\r}

606
01:03:25,720 --> 01:03:30,806
當我跪在你的床邊時，
3，700年前。
{\fs12}as I knelt by your bed,
3,700 years ago.{\r}

607
01:03:30,880 --> 01:03:35,408
從來沒有人遭受過任何苦難
女人，因為你為我受苦。
{\fs12}No man has ever suffered for
woman as you suffered for me.{\r}

608
01:03:36,080 --> 01:03:37,681
而現在，眾神
原諒我們...
{\fs12}And now that the gods
have forgiven us...{\r}

609
01:03:37,720 --> 01:03:39,370
不，不，還沒有。
{\fs12}No, no, not yet.{\r}

610
01:03:40,680 --> 01:03:42,921
你的靈魂是一個凡人的身體，
{\fs12}Your soul is in a mortal body,{\r}

611
01:03:44,000 --> 01:03:47,482
自那以後多次更新
我們喜歡在舊的底比斯。
{\fs12}renewed many times since
we loved in Thebes of old.{\r}

612
01:03:48,760 --> 01:03:52,321
但那種愛不適合我們
再一次，直到偉大的變化。
{\fs12}But that love is not for us
again until the great change.{\r}

613
01:03:53,440 --> 01:03:55,249
我不明白。
{\fs12}I do not understand.{\r}

614
01:04:01,640 --> 01:04:02,766
看。
{\fs12}Look.{\r}

615
01:04:14,120 --> 01:04:15,884
看，想知道。
{\fs12}Look and wonder.{\r}

616
01:04:16,760 --> 01:04:18,444
我自己的身影。
{\fs12}Figure of myself.{\r}

617
01:04:18,520 --> 01:04:21,808
這是我的棺材，由我的棺材製成
父親反對我的死。
{\fs12}It is my coffin, made by my
father against my death.{\r}

618
01:04:23,520 --> 01:04:26,171
什麼木乃伊篡奪了我的
永恆的安息之所？
{\fs12}What mummy has usurped my
eternal resting place?{\r}

619
01:04:26,240 --> 01:04:28,208
這是你的死殼。
{\fs12}It is thy dead shell.{\r}

620
01:04:28,280 --> 01:04:31,762
我試著提出這個
身體。我現在可以提高它。
{\fs12}I tried then to raise this
body. I could raise it now.{\r}

621
01:04:32,400 --> 01:04:36,450
但這只是一件事
在沒有靈魂的情況下，我的意志感動了。
{\fs12}But it would be a mere thing that
moved at my will, without a soul.{\r}

622
01:05:14,760 --> 01:05:18,242
這不僅僅是這個身體
我喜歡的。這是你的靈魂。
{\fs12}It was not only this body
that I loved. It was thy soul.{\r}

623
01:05:18,320 --> 01:05:20,607
我毀掉了這個沒有生氣的東西。
{\fs12}I destroy this lifeless thing.{\r}

624
01:05:21,320 --> 01:05:24,483
你取代它的位置
但是片刻之後
{\fs12}Thou shalt take its place
but for a few moments,{\r}

625
01:05:24,560 --> 01:05:29,122
再起來，
即使我已經復活了。
{\fs12}and then rise again,
even as I have risen.{\r}

626
01:05:47,280 --> 01:05:48,361
來。
{\fs12}Come.{\r}

627
01:06:12,760 --> 01:06:16,606
印和闐，這是
屍體的地方。
{\fs12}Imhotep, this is the
place of embalmment.{\r}

628
01:06:17,480 --> 01:06:22,247
這對我來說是不合法的，是女祭司
伊希斯，看到或觸摸一個不潔的東西。
{\fs12}It is not lawful for me, a priestess of
Isis, to see or touch an unclean thing.{\r}

629
01:06:23,080 --> 01:06:26,687
來到阿努比斯的祭壇，
死者的嚮導。
{\fs12}Come to the altar of Anubis,
the guide of the dead.{\r}

630
01:06:37,960 --> 01:06:40,850
時機已到
為了最後的祈禱。
{\fs12}The time has come
for the final prayers.{\r}

631
01:06:40,920 --> 01:06:43,127
我和阿努比斯有什麼關係？
{\fs12}What have I to do with Anubis?{\r}

632
01:06:47,760 --> 01:06:51,082
古老的儀式一定是
在你的身體上表演。
{\fs12}The ancient rites must be
performed over thy body.{\r}

633
01:06:51,160 --> 01:06:52,844
然後我會讀
偉大的咒語
{\fs12}Then I will read
the great spell{\r}

634
01:06:52,920 --> 01:06:56,322
伊希斯帶來的
奧西里斯從墳墓回來。
{\fs12}with which Isis brought
Osiris back from the grave.{\r}

635
01:06:57,200 --> 01:06:59,680
你又要復活了。
{\fs12}And thou shalt rise again.{\r}

636
01:06:59,760 --> 01:07:01,046
沒有。
{\fs12}No.{\r}

637
01:07:01,920 --> 01:07:06,084
不，我還活著！
我年輕！我不會死的！
{\fs12}No, I'm alive!
I'm young! I won't die!{\r}

638
01:07:07,280 --> 01:07:10,727
我曾經愛過你，但現在
你屬於死人。
{\fs12}I loved you once, but now
you belong with the dead.{\r}

639
01:07:11,560 --> 01:07:13,369
我是安克蘇娜姆，
{\fs12}I am Anck-es-en-Amon,{\r}

640
01:07:13,880 --> 01:07:17,043
但是我...我也是其他人。
{\fs12}but I... I'm somebody else, too.{\r}

641
01:07:17,800 --> 01:07:20,565
我想生活，即使在
這個奇怪的新世界。
{\fs12}I want to live, even in
this strange new world.{\r}

642
01:07:20,680 --> 01:07:23,809
為了你的緣故
我活埋了。
{\fs12}For thy sake
I was buried alive.{\r}

643
01:07:23,880 --> 01:07:27,043
我只問你
痛苦的一刻。
{\fs12}I ask of thee only
a moment of agony.{\r}

644
01:07:27,120 --> 01:07:29,566
只有這樣我們才能團結起來。
{\fs12}Only so can we be united.{\r}

645
01:07:34,440 --> 01:07:36,124
natron浴。
{\fs12}The bath of natron.{\r}

646
01:07:37,440 --> 01:07:40,410
你不應該暴跌
我的身體進入那個！
{\fs12}You shall not plunge
my body into that!{\r}

647
01:07:40,480 --> 01:07:42,323
讓契約完成。
{\fs12}Let the deed be done.{\r}

648
01:07:59,720 --> 01:08:02,405
讓我走！
讓我走！
{\fs12}Let me go!
Let me go!{\r}

649
01:08:02,480 --> 01:08:05,643
別殺了我！我是一個
伊希斯的女祭司！
{\fs12}Don't kill me! I'm a
priestess of Isis!{\r}

650
01:08:05,720 --> 01:08:10,123
救我脫離那個木乃伊！
它死了！救救我！
{\fs12}Save me from that mummy!
It's dead! Save me!{\r}

651
01:08:35,080 --> 01:08:38,766
我不再害怕你了。
和我一起做你想做的事
{\fs12}I no longer fear you.
Do with me what you will.{\r}

652
01:08:55,720 --> 01:08:56,881
法蘭克！
{\fs12}Frank!{\r}

653
01:08:57,680 --> 01:08:58,841
法蘭克！
{\fs12}Frank!{\r}

654
01:09:00,080 --> 01:09:03,243
她去了他。
他們必須在博物館。
{\fs12}She's gone to him.
They must be in the museum.{\r}

655
01:09:04,520 --> 01:09:06,727
現在我知道他可怕的計劃。
{\fs12}Now I know his horrible plan.{\r}

656
01:09:07,560 --> 01:09:11,565
他會殺了她並製造
她像個自己一樣活著的木乃伊。
{\fs12}He's going to kill her and make
her a living mummy, like himself.{\r}

657
01:09:24,680 --> 01:09:29,208
眾神將進入黑社會
安克蘇娜姆的精神。{\fs12}The gods will receive into the underworld
the spirit of Anck-es-en-Amon.{\r}

658
01:09:30,400 --> 01:09:32,084
但不長久。
{\fs12}But not for long.{\r}

659
01:09:33,360 --> 01:09:36,921
奧西里斯會釋放你的靈魂。
{\fs12}Osiris will release thy soul.{\r}

660
01:09:50,440 --> 01:09:52,807
你將從生活中休息，
{\fs12}You shall rest from life,{\r}

661
01:09:52,880 --> 01:09:55,281
喜歡夕陽
在西方。
{\fs12}like the setting sun
in the West.{\r}

662
01:09:56,040 --> 01:09:58,202
但是你會重新開始
在東方
{\fs12}But you shall dawn anew
in the East{\r}

663
01:09:58,280 --> 01:10:01,966
作為第一縷曙光
Amon-Ra驅散陰影。
{\fs12}as the first rays of
Amon-Ra dispel the shadows.{\r}

664
01:10:14,680 --> 01:10:16,842
看！那是什麼？
{\fs12}Look! What's that?{\r}

665
01:10:20,160 --> 01:10:21,446
來吧！
{\fs12}Come on!{\r}

666
01:10:32,160 --> 01:10:33,650
法蘭克！法蘭克！
{\fs12}Frank! Frank!{\r}

667
01:10:43,400 --> 01:10:44,890
海倫！
{\fs12}Helen!{\r}

668
01:10:45,840 --> 01:10:47,001
海倫！
{\fs12}Helen!{\r}

669
01:10:48,840 --> 01:10:50,001
海倫！
{\fs12}Helen!{\r}

670
01:10:56,160 --> 01:10:57,924
哦，伊希斯！神聖的少女！
{\fs12}Oh, Isis! Holy Maiden!{\r}

671
01:10:58,000 --> 01:11:02,050
我是你奉獻的外衣。
我打破了我的誓言。救救我吧！
{\fs12}I was thy consecrated vestal.
I broke my vows. Save me now!{\r}

672
01:11:02,120 --> 01:11:05,602
教我古老的召喚，
我忘記的神聖咒語。
{\fs12}Teach me the ancient summons,
the holy spells I've forgotten.{\r}

673
01:11:05,680 --> 01:11:07,762
我一如既往地叫你！
{\fs12}I call upon thee as of old!{\r}

674
01:12:04,640 --> 01:12:05,846
海倫。
{\fs12}Helen.{\r}

675
01:12:07,760 --> 01:12:10,570
叫她。他拖了
她回到古埃及。
{\fs12}Call her. He has dragged
her back to Ancient Egypt.{\r}

676
01:12:10,680 --> 01:12:14,241
叫她！她的愛
你可能會跨越幾個世紀。
{\fs12}Call her! Her love for
you may bridge the centuries.{\r}

677
01:12:14,880 --> 01:12:17,042
海倫。海倫！
{\fs12}Helen. Helen!{\r}

678
01:12:18,080 --> 01:12:20,560
回來。
這是法蘭克。
{\fs12}Come back.
It's Frank.{\r}

679
01:12:21,760 --> 01:12:23,091
回來
{\fs12}Come back.{\r}


